Introduction

Y&W (Korean: 영앤와일드; Japanese: ヤング＆ワイルド; short for Young and Wild) is a four-member boy group under INAKIST Entertainment. They consist of 4 members: Woojoo, Minsu, Ino and Eunjae.They debuted on July 18, 2020 with their first digital single "Walk With Me".
